description:
As a Shopline

  and cart has some product then click buy now button in wishlist

steps.name: I am on Admin Login Page
I fill correct account email to email field
I fill correct account password to password field
I click on login button
I should see successful login
I check intercom message notification frame and click clear intercom message button
I check intercom message notification frame and click intercom message close button
I check new feature alert notification frame and click new feature alert close button
I check and click no thanks button
I am on Shop Login Layout V Two Page
I fill email to email field
I fill password to password field
I click on submit button
I should be redirected to Shop Home Layout V Two Page
I am on Shop Product Index Layout V Two Page
I hover over search icon
I input "Out Of Stock" to search field
1st product of products list should contain 'Out Of Stock'
I click on 1st product of products list
I should be redirected to Shop Product Show Layout V Two Page
I should see sold out
I should see notify when in stock button
I should see add to wishlist button off
I click on add to wishlist button off
I should see alert
alert should contain "When product is back in stock, there will be email notification."
